extends ./base.jade

block content
	.jumbotron.jumbotron-fluid.bg-info
		.container.text-sm-center.p-t-3
			h1.display-2 Full Stack Conf
			p.lead A One-day Conference About All Things JavaScript!
			.btn-group.m-t-2(role='group', aria-label='Basic example')
				button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(type='button', data-toggle='modal', data-target='#register') Register Now
				a.btn.btn-secondary.btn-lg(href='#speakers') See Speakers
	.container.p-t-2
		#about.row
			.col-lg-4.col-lg-push-4
				h3.m-b-2 About Full Stack Conf
				img.m-b-1.img-fluid.img-rounded.hidden-xs-down(src='http://lilianabrissos.com/img/projects/pdx.jpg', alt='Portland')
				p
				| The beautiful city of Portland, Oregon will be the host city for Full Stack Conf!
				p
				| Explore the future of JavaScript with a lineup of industry professionals. Discover new techniques to advance your career as a web developer.
			.col-lg-4.col-lg-pull-4
				h3.m-b-2 Expert Speakers
				p
				| Our expert speaker lineup was just announced, so don't wait too long before grabbing your tickets!
				p
				| Want to meet the international JavaScript community and share skills with some of the world's top experts, hackers, and makers? Be the first to know what to expect for the future of JavaScript.
				p
				| Full Stack Conf is committed to being inclusive and welcoming for everyone. We look forward to another intensive day of learning and sharing.
			.col-lg-4
				h3.m-b-2 What You'll Learn
				.list-group
				a.list-group-item(href='#')
					strong MongoDB
					| : NoSQL database
				a.list-group-item(href='#')
					strong Angular
					| : JavaScript framework
				a.list-group-item(href='#')
					strong Express
					| : Framework for Node
				a.list-group-item(href='#')
					strong Node.js
					| : JavaScript environment
				a.list-group-item(href='#')
					strong ES2015
					| : Latest version of JavaScript
				a.list-group-item(href='#')
					strong Babel
					| : JavaScript compiler
		h1#speakers.display-4.text-xs-center.m-y-3.text-muted Speakers
		.row
			.col-md-6.col-lg-4
				.card
				img.card-img-top.img-fluid(src='http://lilianabrissos.com/img/projects/angie.png', alt='Card image cap')
				.card-block
					h4.card-title Angie McAngular
					p.card-text
					| Angie is a web developer and teacher who is passionate about building scalable, data driven web apps, especially ones that address old problems with new tech!
			.col-md-6.col-lg-4
				.card
				img.card-img-top.img-fluid(src='http://lilianabrissos.com/img/projects/nodestradamus.png', alt='Card image cap')
				.card-block
					h4.card-title NodeStradamus
					p.card-text
					| "NodeStra" is a software engineer and philosopher trying to leave the world better than he found it. He codes for non-profits, eCommerce, and large-scale web apps.
			.col-md-6.col-lg-4
				.card
				img.card-img-top.img-fluid(src='http://lilianabrissos.com/img/projects/geo.png', alt='Card image cap')
				.card-block
					h4.card-title Geo "Lo" Cation
					p.card-text
					| Geo is a JavaScript developer working on large-scale applications. He's also a teacher who strives to support students in removing all barriers to learning code.
			.col-md-6.col-lg-4
				.card
				img.card-img-top.img-fluid(src='http://lilianabrissos.com/img/projects/ecma.png', alt='Card image cap')
				.card-block
					h4.card-title Ecma Scriptnstuff
					p.card-text
					| Ecma found her passion for computers and programming over 15 years ago. She is excited to introduce people to the wonderful world of JavaScript.
			.col-md-6.col-lg-4
				.card
				img.card-img-top.img-fluid(src='http://lilianabrissos.com/img/projects/jay.png', alt='Card image cap')
				.card-block
					h4.card-title Jay Query
					p.card-text
					| Jay is a developer, author of CSS: The Missing Manual, JavaScript & jQuery: The Missing Manual, and web development teacher.
			.col-md-6.col-lg-4
				.card
				img.card-img-top.img-fluid(src='http://lilianabrissos.com/img/projects/json.png', alt='Card image cap')
				.card-block
					h4.card-title Json Babel
					p.card-text
					| All of his professional life, Json has worked with computers online; he is a polyglot programmer and likes using the right tools for the job.
			
		h1#schedule.display-4.text-xs-center.m-y-3.text-muted Schedule
		ul.list-group
			li.list-group-item
				h4.list-group-item-heading
				| Keynote: Internet of Things 
				span.label.label-info.label-pill.pull-xs-right 9:00am
				| 					NodeStradamus
			li.list-group-item
				h4.list-group-item-heading
				| Angular Basics 
				span.label.label-info.label-pill.pull-xs-right 10:00am
				| 					Angie McAngular
			li.list-group-item
				h4.list-group-item-heading
				| Hey, Mongo! 
				span.label.label-info.label-pill.pull-xs-right 11:00am
				| 					Jay Query
			li.list-group-item.list-group-item-success
				h4.list-group-item-heading
				| Lunch 
				span.label.label-info.label-pill.pull-xs-right 12:00pm
				| 					Free pizza for everyone!
			li.list-group-item
				h4.list-group-item-heading
				| Introducing ES2015 
				span.label.label-info.label-pill.pull-xs-right 1:00pm
				| 			  	Ecma Scriptnstuff
			li.list-group-item
				h4.list-group-item-heading
				| Gettin' MEAN 
				span.label.label-info.label-pill.pull-xs-right 2:00pm
				| 			    Geo "Lo" Cation
			li.list-group-item
				h4.list-group-item-heading
				| What's Babel? 
				span.label.label-info.label-pill.pull-xs-right 3:00pm
				| 			    Json Babel
			
		button.btn.btn-info-outline.btn-lg.center-block.m-y-3(type='button', data-toggle='modal', data-target='#register') Don't Miss Out, Register Now

		hr
		.row.p-y-2.text-muted
			.col-md-6.col-xl-5
				p
				strong About Treehouse
				p
				| Treehouse brings affordable technology education to people everywhere to help them achieve their dreams and change the world.
			.col-md-6.col-xl-5.col-xl-offset-2
				p
				strong Stay up-to-date on Full Stack Conf
				.input-group
				input.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Email')
				span.input-group-btn
					button.btn.btn-primary(type='button') Sign up
		hr
		.row.p-y-1
			.col-md-7
				ul.nav.nav-inline
				li.nav-item
					a.nav-link(href='#') Community
				li.nav-item
					a.nav-link(href='#') Tracks
				li.nav-item
					// Split button
					.btn-group.dropup
					button.btn.btn-secondary(type='button') Other Confs
					button.btn.btn-secondary.dropdown-toggle(type='button', data-toggle='dropdown', aria-haspopup='true', aria-expanded='false')
						span.sr-only Toggle Dropdown
					.dropdown-menu
						a.dropdown-item(href='#') CSS Conf
						a.dropdown-item(href='#') Python Conf
						a.dropdown-item(href='#') Java Conf
						a.dropdown-item(href='#') Swift Conf
			.col-md-5.text-md-right
				small © 2016 Full Stack Conf & Treehouse
		// /footer
	
	#register.modal.fade
		.modal-dialog.modal-lg(role='document')
		.modal-content
			.modal-header
			button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal', aria-label='Close')
				span(aria-hidden='true') ×
			h4.modal-title Register for Full Stack Conf
			.modal-body
			p Form goes here...
			.modal-footer
			button.btn.btn-secondary(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') Close
			button.btn.btn-primary(type='button') Save changes
		// /.modal-content
		// /.modal-dialog
